OL,3,CWoman dies in dog attack in Essex
OL,5,FA 19-year old woman has died following
OL,6,Fan incident involving a dog at a house
OL,7,Fin Dunmow.
OL,9,FEssex police confirmed they were
OL,10,Fcalled to an address in Leaden Roding
OL,11,Fat 10.45 pm on Friday, April 10, where
OL,12,Fthey found a 19-year-old woman with
OL,13,Fserious injuries.
OL,15,FDespite emergency services' efforts,
OL,16,Fshe was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
