OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775995869
OL,3,CWoman dies in dog attack in Essex
OL,5,FPolice have been carrying out
OL,6,Fenquiries to establish the
OL,7,Fcircumstances, and believe she had
OL,8,Fbeen attacked by a dog at the property
OL,9,Fin Long Hide.
OL,11,FSpecialist officers ensured the scene
OL,12,Fwas safe and seized the dog.
OL,14,FA 37-year-old man from Dunmow has been
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of being in
OL,16,Fcharge of a dog dangerously out of
OL,17,Fcontrol and causing injury resulting
OL,18,Fin death. He is currently in custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
