OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775995869
OL,3,CWoman dies in dog attack in Essex
OL,5,FAssistant Chief Constable Stuart
OL,6,FHooper said: "I know this incident
OL,7,Fwill be a shock to the local community.
OL,9,F"My thoughts, and those of us all at
OL,10,FEssex Police, are with the loved ones
OL,11,Fof the woman who died yesterday.
OL,13,F"We will have officers in the area
OL,14,Fthroughout today, so please come and
OL,15,Fspeak to them if you have any
OL,16,Finformation or have any concerns.
OL,18,F"Experienced detectives are leading
OL,19,Fthe investigation to understand
OL,20,Fexactly what has happened."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
